name: Banks The Squid
description:
~Bank$ The Squid~
Play as a Squid representing FaZe Banks himself, shooting out stacks of money to defeat enemies.
Collect piles of money to save up for upgrades and extra lives to survive even longer!

Features:
-Starting with 10 puzzle filled levels (many more to come)
-Unique upgrade system(more to come)
-A sick adventure
-A very large urge to start spitting stacks of money ;)



Disclaimer:
This game is a fan-made game and is no way, shape, or form, affiliated with FaZe Clan.
For entertainment/enjoyment purposes.

Complete thanks go out to Ricky Banks for complete inspiration on the game, i hope you enjoy it as much as i enjoyed making it for you.
